Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.66,0:00:05.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,弹奏吧！光之美少女 转调
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.72,0:00:17.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,传送吧！两人的组曲
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.56,0:00:23.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,组曲 光之美少女
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.23,0:00:27.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,赛莲唷
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.90,0:00:29.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,梅菲斯特大人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.78,0:00:30.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,之前那次明明是取得
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.98,0:00:32.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大量音符的大好机会
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.95,0:00:33.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是你却失手了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.40,0:00:36.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊！梅菲斯特大人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.78,0:00:37.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再让赛莲做领队的话
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.95,0:00:40.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,说不定又让音符给跑掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.41,0:00:43.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我可不会再犯这样错误！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.96,0:00:46.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,让音符跑掉的又不是我们
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.83,0:00:47.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对吧！！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.83,0:00:48.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别故意讲出来让我听到
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.96,0:00:50.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不论是谁放跑的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.96,0:00:52.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,结论就是一切
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.97,0:00:56.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小组失败可是领队该负起的责任啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.97,0:00:57.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,赛莲
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.97,0:00:58.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我了解
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.93,0:01:00.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为了完成领队的责任
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.93,0:01:03.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我回顾至目前为止与光之美少女的战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.93,0:01:05.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,制定计策
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.94,0:01:06.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为蛮忙我就先告退了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.94,0:01:08.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊！喂！我还没......
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.36,0:01:13.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯！应当能看得出来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.94,0:01:14.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,光之美少女的弱点
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.95,0:01:17.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,光之美少女弱点 光之美少女弱点
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.74,0:01:19.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,弱点 弱点
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.87,0:01:22.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,弱点 弱点 弱点 弱点 弱点
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.95,0:01:28.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,绝对不可以原谅！！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.13,0:01:32.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.75,0:01:33.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是这个！！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.01,0:01:37.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啦?啦?啦?啦?啦?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.89,0:01:40.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,组曲 组曲光之美少女?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.10,0:01:43.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,组曲 光之美少女
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.39,0:01:47.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,组曲 组曲光之美少女?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.39,0:01:49.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,组曲 光之美少女
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.94,0:01:56.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,响彻着的旋律
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.36,0:02:02.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如今已经开始了故事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.37,0:02:09.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,风铃声鸣响 聆听的音涌现他们的双脚
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.30,0:02:13.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,将节奏刻印一曲在我身上 愉快的小调
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.01,0:02:18.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大声地唱起歌吧！（OK!)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.88,0:02:21.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,犬儿大步地踏着柔和音调！（汪！）
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.76,0:02:24.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一起拍打手拍子哟！音乐！（光之美少女！）
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.52,0:02:28.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,做了这样许多地重复去吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.02,0:02:31.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,唱歌吧！在这个世界内
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.02,0:02:34.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,摆动吧！大家彼此心连地
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.86,0:02:36.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为了你（为了我）
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.36,0:02:37.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为了女孩（为了男孩）
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.28,0:02:40.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,八度跳跃地飞过音阶
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.95,0:02:43.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,梦想！往者明日迈进
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.12,0:02:47.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,相信！羽翼双飞翔之间
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.08,0:02:53.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奏响着 笑容绽放面孔的 音调！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.34,0:02:57.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,组曲 组曲 光之美少女?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.70,0:03:10.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喀喀~ ~！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.87,0:03:13.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喵喵！喀喀~有味道咪
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.29,0:03:15.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喵~哈！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.96,0:03:18.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喀喀喀喀~在这附近喵！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.96,0:03:21.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喀喀~啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.96,0:03:22.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有了喵
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.96,0:03:24.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真幸运喵！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.97,0:03:29.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊呀！？赛莲
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.93,0:03:33.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个音符
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.93,0:03:35.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是哈米先找到的 喵
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.94,0:03:42.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 喵？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.94,0:03:44.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我做错了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.94,0:03:47.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的想与哈米再一次结为朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.95,0:03:50.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一直以来做了很过分的事真的对不起！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.95,0:03:52.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能原谅我吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.00,0:03:54.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,赛莲...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.60,0:03:55.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,当然啦喵
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.56,0:03:57.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一起收集音符
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.83,0:04:00.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一起演唱幸福的旋律吧 喵
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.92,0:04:02.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.97,0:04:09.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊~呀！啊呀呀呀呀...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.32,0:04:14.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要做什么喵？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.93,0:04:16.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,竟然这么简单就骗到啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.93,0:04:19.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还是如同往常天然傻呆的小猫呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.94,0:04:21.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,赛莲与哈米是朋友 喵
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.36,0:04:23.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哼！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.94,0:04:27.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想成为朋友什么的当然是骗人的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.94,0:04:30.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算有朋友总有一日一定会被背叛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.95,0:04:33.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我根本不相信朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.96,0:04:42.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,出来吧 负向音调
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.68,0:05:00.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,负向音调
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.77,0:05:07.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咕腻咕腻！光之美少女无法变身喵?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.78,0:05:13.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,响 今天甜点部要试做新口味的甜点
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.74,0:05:14.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要来吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.74,0:05:15.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯！我去我去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.99,0:05:17.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哈米也可以去吗？喵
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.46,0:05:20.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哈米！？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.00,0:05:22.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喵哈
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.00,0:05:24.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,呐...要做出怎样的甜点啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.00,0:05:26.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,敬请期待它的完成吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.96,0:05:28.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哼！说不定会很难吃呢 喵
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.13,0:05:30.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.97,0:05:31.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为是试做的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.97,0:05:33.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以不见得会好吃 喵
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.97,0:05:35.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,过于期待的话将大失所望哟 喵
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.26,0:05:36.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喵~ ~哈哈！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.97,0:05:38.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哈米你怎么啦？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.97,0:05:40.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你背后怎么有没见过的气息...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.94,0:05:51.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哈米！稍微在这里等待一会喔
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.11,0:05:52.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,响你过来一下 咦 啊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.95,0:05:54.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奏 怎么啦 怎么啦？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.95,0:05:58.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嘻嘻
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.95,0:06:00.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那一个才不是真的哈米呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.95,0:06:02.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦！？不是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.96,0:06:03.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你过来看一看喔
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.96,0:06:09.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那一条项链
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.97,0:06:17.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.76,0:06:19.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,至目前为止赛莲所变成的人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.97,0:06:21.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都戴着那条项链
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.98,0:06:22.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.98,0:06:24.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个是赛莲！？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.94,0:06:29.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在计谋着什么呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.94,0:06:33.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,它一定又想让我们俩吵架
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.95,0:06:34.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.95,0:06:37.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真正的哈米恐怕不在这
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.95,0:06:40.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很有可能被她抓住了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.74,0:06:42.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,若冒险出手恐怕哈米将有危险
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.75,0:06:43.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.96,0:06:46.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只能先装作被骗的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.96,0:06:47.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,稍微看一下情况吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.96,0:06:49.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样子太费时了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.96,0:06:51.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,先抓住赛莲问出哈米的下落
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.96,0:06:52.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,会比较快啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.96,0:06:54.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,急躁地去行动
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.67,0:06:55.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要是哈米发生什么事情该怎么办啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.76,0:06:56.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,悠闲地去行动
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.76,0:06:58.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要是哈米万一发生什么事该怎么办啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.76,0:07:00.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.77,0:07:09.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯...稍微等一下！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.77,0:07:13.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,赛莲的目的是使我们俩吵起来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.94,0:07:16.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是我们该吵架的时间啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.95,0:07:19.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是呢 接下来该怎样做？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.95,0:07:21.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在先装作被骗的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.95,0:07:25.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然后搜寻出哈米的所在位置对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.96,0:07:27.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,呐！我说哈米
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.96,0:07:28.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊！什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.96,0:07:31.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今日来这边之前去了哪边呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.96,0:07:32.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喵啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.96,0:07:34.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,做了什么可疑的事情吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.05,0:07:35.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,稍微等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.80,0:07:36.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哈米
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.97,0:07:39.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在搞什么啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.97,0:07:41.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那种演技是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.76,0:07:43.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很容易马上就被察觉到可疑哟
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.77,0:07:44.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没办法啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.56,0:07:46.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我最不擅长说谎话啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.77,0:07:48.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,难道就不能想想别的办法吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.77,0:07:50.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我已经尽全力在做了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.77,0:07:52.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,说到底是奏......
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.77,0:07:53.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了吗？喵
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.78,0:07:54.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,呃！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.78,0:07:56.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没有 什么事都...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.78,0:07:57.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没有哟
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.74,0:08:02.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有音符的味道 喵
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.96,0:08:08.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊！稍微等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.96,0:08:11.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 响
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.75,0:08:12.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.76,0:08:18.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦！到哪里去了？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.76,0:08:21.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,响！？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.77,0:08:26.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.98,0:08:30.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.98,0:08:32.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,响的足球
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.94,0:08:33.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,南野同学
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.77,0:08:35.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老师
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.94,0:08:36.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,刚刚响 啊 不是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.94,0:08:38.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,北条同学刚刚有没有来过这呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.95,0:08:39.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,北条同学的话
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.74,0:08:42.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,往那边了！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.95,0:08:44.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.75,0:08:50.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦！？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.96,0:08:53.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老师你一直是戴着项链的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.04,0:08:55.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊~ ~
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.13,0:08:57.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么？？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.81,0:09:07.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哼...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.77,0:09:10.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,响和奏迟早会出现来救我的 喵
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.98,0:09:12.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是不可能发生的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.98,0:09:14.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喵！？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.94,0:09:18.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,呵呵
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.95,0:09:21.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喵！赛莲
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.95,0:09:24.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那两个人再也不能变成光之美少女
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.95,0:09:26.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喵！？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.75,0:09:34.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这里是...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.75,0:09:35.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哪里啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.75,0:09:37.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.96,0:09:38.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是出口吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.59,0:09:41.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.97,0:09:43.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都是因为奏采取这样拐弯抹角的作战策略咯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.76,0:09:46.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,响！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.97,0:09:48.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在哪里？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.77,0:09:51.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.98,0:09:53.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,竟然碰到这种事情
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.73,0:09:55.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喔
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.94,0:09:58.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,出口吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.69,0:10:00.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,趯 趯 趯 趯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.69,0:10:02.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,趯 趯 趯 趯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.45,0:10:08.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,~
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.74,0:10:09.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊~
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.74,0:10:12.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们两人各自被关在异空间中了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.96,0:10:13.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哈米！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.96,0:10:14.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是你的话
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.83,0:10:15.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,应该能够明白吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.33,0:10:18.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那两人已经没有可以变身的方式了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.96,0:10:20.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,噗喵喵
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.89,0:10:39.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,后半段开始放送
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.40,0:10:42.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,呃呵呵
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.94,0:10:44.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如此一来碍事的人就不能来啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.95,0:10:47.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们的胜利是指日可待了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.95,0:10:49.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是漂亮的作战呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.95,0:10:52.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,虽然还远不及我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.95,0:10:54.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯~嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.96,0:10:56.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.84,0:10:59.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊！啊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.84,0:11:01.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别拿那么多啊！！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.88,0:11:03.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.97,0:11:06.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哈米我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.89,0:11:08.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也很想吃牛肉火锅 喵
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.93,0:11:09.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喵！？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.93,0:11:12.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,呷呷~呷呷~
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.93,0:11:13.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,呷~呷~
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.93,0:11:16.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吃的话会变胖喔
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.94,0:11:17.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嘿喵
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.94,0:11:21.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个味道的香菇也是很美味呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.86,0:11:23.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好香的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.99,0:11:24.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,负向音调哟
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.36,0:11:27.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,作为开始
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.95,0:11:30.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,让这间学校的学生们变得不幸吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.95,0:11:31.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,负向音调！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.83,0:11:48.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好悲伤啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.76,0:11:51.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个声音！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.93,0:11:54.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,学校内大家的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.81,0:11:56.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.85,0:11:59.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,弹奏吧！光之美少女 转调
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.94,0:12:01.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦！？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.94,0:12:05.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,弹奏吧！光之美少女 转调
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.94,0:12:06.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我说
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.95,0:12:07.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这不就没办法变身了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.95,0:12:09.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.86,0:12:10.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,难道是咪利不在吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.95,0:12:12.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.95,0:12:15.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是因为你们的内心都七零八落
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.95,0:12:16.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个声音是...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.83,0:12:17.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,赛莲！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.96,0:12:18.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯呵呵
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.75,0:12:20.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看了许多次
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.96,0:12:21.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们变身那一段
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.92,0:12:23.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就发现到了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.92,0:12:29.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,绝对不可以原谅！！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.93,0:12:30.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一直都必须要声音
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.93,0:12:33.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,同步的时候才能变身
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.93,0:12:34.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊！！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.93,0:12:36.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要变为光之美少女
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.72,0:12:38.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,必须要两人的心同步才行
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.94,0:12:39.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那么把你们
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.94,0:12:43.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,关在不同的位置不就好了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.82,0:12:45.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,变不成光之美少女的你们
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.90,0:12:47.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是绝不可能从那里逃出的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.99,0:12:49.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯呵呵...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.90,0:12:51.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喫喫~喫喫
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.91,0:12:54.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喫喫喫喫~喫喫喫喫
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.91,0:12:56.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯...嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.91,0:12:59.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.91,0:13:01.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家只要哀伤起来就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.92,0:13:02.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喫喫~喫喫
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.92,0:13:04.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,赛莲住手啊 喵
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.92,0:13:06.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,赛莲你不是这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.92,0:13:07.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,坏孩子啊 喵
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.81,0:13:08.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.81,0:13:09.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哈米
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.92,0:13:11.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你明白什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.93,0:13:12.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,当然了 喵
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.93,0:13:14.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哈米与赛莲是好朋友 喵
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.93,0:13:17.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果有时间讲这些无聊的话
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.22,0:13:18.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊喵
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.81,0:13:20.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还不如担心一下自己吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.94,0:13:21.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为光之美少女已经
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.94,0:13:22.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不会再出来啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.94,0:13:24.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这可就不好讲 Dodo
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.90,0:13:30.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在那里！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.90,0:13:32.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,缪斯天使
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.82,0:13:33.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,又来碍事了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.70,0:13:35.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dodo
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.91,0:13:40.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不是任何人的伙伴 DoDo
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.83,0:13:41.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.91,0:13:43.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把无辜的人牵连进来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.92,0:13:45.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我可无法坐视不管 Dodo
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.92,0:13:46.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么！！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.81,0:13:47.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,给我上
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.55,0:13:48.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,负向音调！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.85,0:14:03.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊~啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.90,0:14:05.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊！！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.94,0:14:07.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.73,0:14:09.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.90,0:14:10.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是音壁 DoDo
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.90,0:14:13.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能将音调全部反弹回去 Dodo
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.91,0:14:14.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,给我上啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.70,0:14:16.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,负向音调！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.93,0:14:39.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.93,0:14:42.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没能够完全地保护住 DoDo
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.94,0:14:46.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,又是哭泣的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.94,0:14:48.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,得做点什么事才行
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.90,0:14:51.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抌啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.95,0:14:55.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抌！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.91,0:14:59.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是在这样地方
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.91,0:15:01.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,磨蹭的时间
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.91,0:15:03.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,缪斯天使
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.91,0:15:05.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快点放弃吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.92,0:15:07.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一个人来太勉强了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.83,0:15:08.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那两人也是不会出来的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.92,0:15:09.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是我赢了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.79,0:15:10.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那两人会怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.88,0:15:12.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就看她们两个了 Dodo
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.91,0:15:13.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.97,0:15:14.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是真正的光之美少女的话
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.97,0:15:15.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不管发生什么事情
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.97,0:15:17.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,绝对不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.93,0:15:21.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奏是绝对不会放弃的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.93,0:15:22.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,响的话
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.93,0:15:24.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,听到大家哭的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.93,0:15:26.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这么地悲伤难过...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.98,0:15:30.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不可能什么都不做
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.90,0:15:33.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.28,0:15:36.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抌 抌啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.99,0:15:40.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们是光之美少女
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.20,0:15:45.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.91,0:15:46.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,DoDo
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.33,0:15:50.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喵噗！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.96,0:15:53.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是响与奏 喵
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.88,0:15:55.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,竟然使大家都悲伤起来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.97,0:15:57.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,绝对不可以原谅
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.76,0:15:59.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dodo
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.89,0:16:00.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rere
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.81,0:16:06.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,弹奏吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.77,0:16:10.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,光之美少女 转调！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.77,0:16:55.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,指尖弹奏的是狂野的曲调
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.15,0:16:58.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,旋律天使
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.53,0:17:04.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,指尖弹奏的是柔和的曲调
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.10,0:17:06.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,节奏天使
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.54,0:17:08.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,传送吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.54,0:17:10.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,两人的组曲
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.67,0:17:14.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,组曲
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.59,0:17:15.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,光之美少女
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.47,0:17:19.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿摵！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.01,0:17:20.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.59,0:17:21.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,褪！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.51,0:17:22.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.84,0:17:23.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,旋律
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.97,0:17:25.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都因为你上了这样明显的当
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.97,0:17:29.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,节奏你才是制定那样麻烦的计策
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.06,0:17:31.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,说到底 认为自己才是正确的此点
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.98,0:17:32.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还是赶快改一改好不好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.13,0:17:33.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你才是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.94,0:17:36.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,多考虑一下别人再行动啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.13,0:17:40.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.93,0:17:41.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,正忙着
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.93,0:17:42.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别碍事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.87,0:17:48.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嘻哧！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.70,0:17:50.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么一回事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.04,0:17:51.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们明明在争吵
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.83,0:17:52.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,却很合拍
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.96,0:17:54.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很合拍
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.96,0:17:55.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,合拍
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.54,0:17:57.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有破绽
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.59,0:17:59.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊！！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.97,0:18:03.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哈米你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.97,0:18:05.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没事 喵
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.76,0:18:06.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你 喵
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.68,0:18:09.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.97,0:18:10.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明明只是在争吵
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.98,0:18:11.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么 为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.77,0:18:14.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我只是对节奏把想说的话
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.85,0:18:15.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全都痛快地说出来罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.94,0:18:18.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,旋律的话就算对她说了真心话
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.94,0:18:19.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.94,0:18:22.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个就是好朋友 喵
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.40,0:18:23.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,趵！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.71,0:18:28.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,呵！成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.04,0:18:31.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不只是声音同步就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.93,0:18:33.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dodo
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.08,0:18:34.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,即使是争吵
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.04,0:18:36.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,即使是在分开的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.96,0:18:37.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,心合二为一的话
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.92,0:18:38.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就能再次变身
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.75,0:18:39.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这就是光之美少女
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.96,0:18:40.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,DoDo
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.97,0:18:53.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,将两个音调力量
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.98,0:18:54.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,合二为一
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.23,0:18:57.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奏响吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.81,0:18:59.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奇迹般的旋律
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.90,0:19:03.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奇迹指挥棒
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.99,0:19:05.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,交叉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.74,0:19:08.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,印刻吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.82,0:19:10.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,伟大般的节奏
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.75,0:19:14.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,幻想指挥棒
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.00,0:19:16.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,交叉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.67,0:19:20.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,飞翔吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.84,0:19:22.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和声的高音谱光环
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.18,0:19:29.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,音乐圆舞曲
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.93,0:19:33.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,超级四重奏
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.90,0:19:43.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,预~备！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.78,0:19:45.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,终曲
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.91,0:19:52.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,呀...眯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.26,0:20:10.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fally
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.97,0:20:15.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再过不久幸福的旋律
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.47,0:20:15.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就要诞生了 喵
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.98,0:20:21.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,坏事就到此结束哟
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.90,0:20:23.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,又要被梅菲斯特大人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.23,0:20:28.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,责备了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.78,0:20:31.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,认命吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.74,0:20:32.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,DoDo
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.08,0:20:34.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吒！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.95,0:20:35.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,赛莲！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.96,0:20:41.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和哈米一起吃杯蛋糕 喵
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.75,0:20:43.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为何我要跟你...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.75,0:20:45.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哈米与赛莲是朋友啊 喵
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.76,0:20:47.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以说想成为朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.76,0:20:48.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都是骗人的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.97,0:20:49.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喵
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.97,0:20:50.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哼！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.97,0:20:52.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是为了骗你而说谎的哟
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.89,0:20:55.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,即使这样
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.68,0:20:58.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哈米一直会是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.68,0:21:00.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,赛莲的朋友 喵
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.69,0:21:07.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吒！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.69,0:21:10.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,朋友什么的怎么能够相信
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.91,0:21:14.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哎喵
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.70,0:21:17.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,消失了 喵
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.91,0:21:19.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.92,0:21:23.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不知何时会变成什么人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.50,0:21:26.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,得小心赛莲才行
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.71,0:21:27.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.88,0:21:29.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,杯蛋糕真好吃 喵
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.01,0:21:32.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想与赛莲一起吃 喵
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.80,0:21:33.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哈米
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.80,0:21:35.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不会生赛莲的气吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.81,0:21:36.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,即使是朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.81,0:21:38.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也会吵架的 喵
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.89,0:21:39.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哈米与赛莲
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.81,0:21:41.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能与响和奏一样
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.81,0:21:43.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,重修旧好的 喵
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.56,0:21:45.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.69,0:21:48.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谁知道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.90,0:21:51.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哈米十分
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.90,0:21:52.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,相信赛莲 喵
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.49,0:21:54.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.79,0:22:01.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,朋友什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.00,0:22:04.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么能够相信
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.43,0:22:17.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,让我们来快乐地弹奏
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.76,0:22:19.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,美妙 强大的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.77,0:22:21.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,音乐！！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.56,0:22:24.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,（呒~！你准备好了吗？）
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.48,0:22:25.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,（是的）
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.98,0:22:29.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,（要上咯！1！2！3！）
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.44,0:22:32.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,组曲光之美少女?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.32,0:22:36.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,呒 呒 呒 呒 呒 呒
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.99,0:22:39.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,组曲光之美少女?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.70,0:22:44.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do Re Mi Fa 到那朵漂浮的天空上（Ryde!)
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.75,0:22:48.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,希望的音调 互相紧靠唷（Dance!)
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.54,0:22:51.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,彩虹色的五线纸上 砰！一步！跳！（愉快！）
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.92,0:22:55.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一群精力充沛的音符们 元气又活力！（好的！）
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.80,0:22:59.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,来游玩吧旋律
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.76,0:23:03.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在的我就是静不下来！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.60,0:23:06.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,来跳舞吧节奏
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.19,0:23:10.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,传达到未来 让我们挑战！前进！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.86,0:23:16.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,光明闪亮的音色
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.41,0:23:19.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,并排相互成列 心中便欣然自喜
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.04,0:23:23.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明日的弹奏也要持续
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.29,0:23:27.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奇妙 强大的 音乐！！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.79,0:23:32.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家一起来唱完
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.38,0:23:34.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,组曲光之美少女?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.81,0:23:43.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哈米
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.60,0:23:44.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不能去
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.35,0:23:45.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你被赛莲骗了啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.14,0:23:47.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没事的 喵
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.94,0:23:48.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们两人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.90,0:23:49.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要一起实现梦想 喵
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.77,0:23:50.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,梦想？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.73,0:23:51.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和赛莲两人合唱
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.69,0:23:53.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,幸福的旋律 喵
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.94,0:23:55.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,赛莲其实是个热爱音乐的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.95,0:23:56.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好孩子 喵
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.28,0:23:58.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哈米！？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.78,0:24:01.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,组曲光之美少女
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.91,0:24:05.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊啊啊啊！赛莲 最后的作战喵?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.70,0:24:07.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,让心中响起
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.79,0:24:08.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和声力量吧！
